videos.description: Baylor's Jo Lual-Acuil gets the open dunk off the pass from Ishmail Wainright.
videos.headline: Baylor opens the scoring with an easy dunk

videos.description: Baylor's Jonathan Motley gets the block against Oklahoma State's Jawun Evans.
videos.headline: Jonathan Motley swats away the Oklahoma State shot

videos.description: Racing behind the Baylor defense, Jeffrey Carroll goes in all alone with the huge tomahawks dunk to extend Oklahoma State's lead in the first half.
videos.headline: Carroll igniting Oklahoma State with tomahawk dunk

videos.description: Baylor's Ishmail Wainright gets the steal, Jonathan Motley makes the contested lay up and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Jonathan Motley makes the contested lay-up with the And-1

videos.description: After Baylor gets the offensive rebound, the Bears good ball movement leads to a Manu Lecomte 3 pointer.
videos.headline: Baylor's Lecomte hits the deep 3 pointer

videos.description: After getting a block, Baylor's Jonathan Motley runs to try and defend Oklahoma State's Cameron McGriff, but fouls him instead.
videos.headline: Jonathan Motley fouls Oklahoma State's Cameron McGriff from 3-point territory

videos.description: Breaking down Baylor's close win against Oklahoma State and the perforamnce from the Bear's Jonathan Motley and Manu Lecomte.
videos.headline: Breaking down Baylor's close game against Oklahoma State
